[SN]TITLE[SN]
The Cheviot, the Stag and the Black, Black Oil goes on tour

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A revival of the iconic 1970s Scottish play "The Cheviot, the Stag and the Black, Black Oil" is beginning a national tour.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
1 September 2016 Last updated at 16:05 BST
The Dundee Rep production was critically acclaimed when it was staged in the city a year ago.
The play was first performed by the 7:84 Theatre company and is an account of Scotland's history from the Highland Clearances to the present day.
